{"tid":1436730,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"通識老師寫給你的抗爭小知識","createTime":"2019-08-09T10:45:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T02:12:23.000Z","uid":267028,"like":167,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"c76aa3954a401623d0e4dbaa4ccfd35daf2589bf","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:45:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>通識老師寫給你的抗爭小知識</strong></span></div><br />\n <br />\n本文作者是一名通識老師，認為通識老師必須政治中立是偽命題。因為如果人沒有立場的話就同咸魚沒有分別，通識老師的責任是讓學生全盤認知社會事實，然後在一個全知的觀點下建立自己的立場，這也是充分而有理據的。對於香港的形勢，想同大家分析下。<br />\n <br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">關於訴求</span></strong></div><br />\n1. 五大訴求邊樣最重要?<br />\n一定係「<span style=\"color: red;\">雙普選</span>」！就係立法會全部議席直選加埋行政長官全民普選。只要做到「雙普選」，餘下的訴求才變得有意義。<br />\n2. 咁，如何達至「雙普選」？<br />\n很簡單，就係支持「一國兩制」、<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">落實</span></span>「基本法」。<br />\n <br />\n<em><span style=\"color: green;\">基本法第45條：行政長官&hellip;最終達至由一個有廣泛代表性的提名委員會按民主程序提名後普選產生的目標。</span></em> <br />\n <br />\n<em><span style=\"color: green;\">基本法第68條：立法會的產生辦法&hellip;最終達至全部議員由普選產生的目標。</span></em><br />\n <br />\n所以我們要既野，從來都已經講左，只係中共無限延遲我們既訴求。既然佢已經講好左，咁就係要提醒佢要落實。所以唔存在甚麼推翻政權、改革政制之類的。記住，係「<span style=\"color: red;\">落實</span>」。《基本法》講左「港人治港」、「高度自治」，我地就係要做返佢講左既野，這是非常合理且出師有命的。咁做亦唔會招人口實，又可以做返一系列長輩圖比藍絲睇。<br />\n<br />\n3. 如何落實「雙普選」？<br />\n從國際形勢睇，要借助美國國會於9月提出的《香港人權和民主法案2019》來<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>推動香港進行雙普選</strong></span>。另外，也靠中美貿易戰的角力而使中共妥協，等佢在香港問題上一直克制，換取得來的就是爭取法案通過的時間。<br />\n <br />\n在香港方面，大家持續性的流水抗爭，政府愈是冷漠、警察愈是愚蠢或無理，就係延續呢場抗爭既最有利條件。我們要有長期作戰既心理準備，唔好因爲身心太累而想盡快結束。我們要持續令政府的管治失效、警察成為過街老鼠，呢d都係增加士氣既彈藥。<br />\n <br />\n由於我地既事已經衝出國際，成為了全球反共、反獨裁的最佳示範。所以，警察愈濫暴，就愈係幫緊件事。就好好將呢d憤怒推上國際。我們需要更多國際支持。<br />\n記住，抗爭時間愈長，對我們愈有利。2020年是關鍵。<br />\n <br />\n關於口號<br />\n1. 口號對了 路就順了<br />\n「<strong><span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 支持一國兩制<br />\n落實雙普選 追究黑警濫暴</span></span></span></strong>」<br />\n <br />\n2. 點解唔嗌「時代革命」？<br />\n <br />\n首先，革命有推翻政權、推翻舊有政制、改革現行的制度的意思。<br />\n現在我們要的是<span style=\"color: red;\">雙普選</span>，這是一直以來寫於基本法內的。因此，我認為這不存在任何政權，甚或制度上的改變或推翻，只是要攞返我地應有既野。所以，「光復香港」就是這個意思。「光復香港」英文譯作&rdquo;Liberate Hong Kong&rdquo; ,有「解救香港」、「給予香港自由/民主」的意思。<br />\n <br />\n至於「時代革命」，「時代」是怎樣「革命」？意思有點含糊。如果係呢個時代需要革命，那「時代」的意思是幾長？10年？50年？那如果這個時代完了，是不是革命也完了？ 如果是這個時代需要革命，那上一個同下一個又需唔需要呢？這是意思上不明確。我唔知英文會點表達，但「革命」一字，自然會連係Revolution.<br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">點解咁執著口號</span></strong>，除左自己要知點解、知道自己爭取緊咩之外，我地仲要<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>俾全世界知香港做緊咩、爭取緊咩</strong></span>。話從中共手中爭取民主、自治權、落實「一個兩制」，呢d全部都係非常合理同正路，因為我地從沒唔係要分裂、唔係要獨立。但如果講「革命」，大家都會變得敏感，是否推翻政權？咁係咪建立新政權？或者有新政制？ 國際對我地既支持就會變得猶豫。<br />\n <br />\n因此，我認為要「光復香港」就已經足夠了。<br />\n <br />\n3. 你可以做咩？<br />\n <br />\n● 先提升自己的政治認知，多睇政治分析文章及書籍，了解自己爭取緊咩及如何爭取。<br />\n● 上網睇到好多片，一定會好嬲。share之前，多做一步，諗下呢樣嘢對於我地既目標係咪有利，分析下先share, <span style=\"color: red;\">幫手宣揚正面能量</span>。<br />\n● 用你的方法去支持任何形式的抗爭，必要時給他們協助。<br />\n<br />\n有什麼唔明既，歡迎提問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd2d54cf7eded9790b229b0a4f152ab35b4343c","tid":1436730,"uid":99546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:52:27.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"f83f35666b119ad0abc4bfd01055379490e45a90","tid":1436730,"uid":259632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:53:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"782c5dd248c5e6b57976592faacdd23a2630e463","tid":1436730,"uid":183302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推一推"},{"pid":"69cf5302d77a0e15b123d1d2c1b1d5e522cae326","tid":1436730,"uid":215341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:53:48.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"070021b40ba19a5c1336518fc18a900d0ffa1901","tid":1436730,"uid":246354,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"你地比ies個評分標準係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b69a0527df1c1e9e1646be636b7797ac8330cb","tid":1436730,"uid":1252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:54:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81f699bd7036f9043c12176a7e22769b2e2f7eb5","tid":1436730,"uid":98273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:55:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd80ae125f27c0bddbaabad6e63eda50e2f52277","tid":1436730,"uid":291279,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:55:47.000Z","msg":"文章有理有節，值得嘉許。<br />\n「光復香港，時代革命」的口號已經深入民心，只能夠是有一個更好的口號才能取而代之。我倒是不認為時代革命這四個字真的是觸動了某些天條。這句話是任由各人去詮釋的。欲加之罪，何患無詞？倒不如是加入一些具體目標在口號裏面，藉此去詮釋抗爭者所說的時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n沒有暴徒，只有暴政<br />\n落實普選，追究黑警<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"15a2ec5c5c01a29466e5ece0a6803a663639cd54","tid":1436730,"uid":215341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:55:48.000Z","msg":"雨傘革命就係革命，時代革命就唔係革命？"},{"pid":"8499d485e4d81f50a923c9ec243a8bc1cb8ef4c1","tid":1436730,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"其實有無人睇過基本法入面講概雙普選？......我睇過但佢話要一個提名委員會認可條友先得，我唔係咁信嗰啲提名委員會"},{"pid":"0cd80a301106a6d64dfafcb378f02f980f10a3c2","tid":1436730,"uid":98729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:01:33.000Z","msg":"推！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fb6df0e757537daa7ec3b01856a2da9122f000c","tid":1436730,"uid":164725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:04:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8d6241e25dde2a09408289a7a233036e60c6260","tid":1436730,"uid":14350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ab72e0c72ca4d6cf34e4300f6e6bc7b4442404","tid":1436730,"uid":36378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:06:10.000Z","msg":"五大訴求缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd74365cefeb9976e5e86a25034bd3c7ae7d4a35","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"15a2ec5c5c01a29466e5ece0a6803a663639cd54","tid":1436730,"uid":215341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:55:48.000Z","msg":"雨傘革命就係革命，時代革命就唔係革命？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:08:19.000Z","msg":"雨傘當時都有人話係運動唔係革命，而且當時雨傘係失敗左既，所以「定性」呢樣嘢要小心。可能大家都知道形式上同革命冇分別，但寫出來就係點present 件事，例如媒體可以拿著「革命」二字來大做文章，佢哋唔會講好多甚麼深層意義野。<br />\n所以如果都用埋「一國兩制」，個效果就會唔同。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f11e3ee9777163076c7f35ae66409c445cee3a6f","tid":1436730,"uid":247198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:10:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06b60397bb3f624f69ae3bfd531af8eb219c23a9","tid":1436730,"uid":266011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1522fc50001fd57aa93bd3009ac2c1782125acc","tid":1436730,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:13:44.000Z","msg":"同政府講落實基本法<br />\n點樣可以避免政府兜返去講廿三條？<br />\n佢哋絕對可以無恥到話依家大部分市民支持全面落實基本法所以依家係時候重推<br />\n到時咪仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93ed3eb9ac67abbf24701b438860f58e5bbf2ba2","tid":1436730,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:14:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83c5aa9f85026903775e514e5dc747fb631827b5","tid":1436730,"uid":302736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"070021b40ba19a5c1336518fc18a900d0ffa1901","tid":1436730,"uid":246354,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"你地比ies個評分標準係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:14:53.000Z","msg":"講真果句個個老師都唔同㗎喎。。<br />\n有D好睇你有冇做問卷呀果D<br />\n我嗰個就話做問卷好浪費時間叫我唔好做"},{"pid":"b9a8029ef9d1dda028920a6087920a830d15de4c","tid":1436730,"uid":299623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:17:31.000Z","msg":"大大力錫落去"},{"pid":"ca8d421354928d52954d5bf27a3dc97561f46844","tid":1436730,"uid":92330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:20:20.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"3ed55c15d018994c4c0f73ceb41c8d0bcb1cbcf3","tid":1436730,"uid":296855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8499d485e4d81f50a923c9ec243a8bc1cb8ef4c1","tid":1436730,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"其實有無人睇過基本法入面講概雙普選？......我睇過但佢話要一個提名委員會認可條友先得，我唔係咁信嗰啲提名委員會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:21:15.000Z","msg":"冇具體講點產生提名委員會，所以都要爭取，不過唔係而家最迫切"},{"pid":"7dd2f4097da757ae279be8d3f57c19a10d38dc77","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"070021b40ba19a5c1336518fc18a900d0ffa1901","tid":1436730,"uid":246354,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"你地比ies個評分標準係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:22:36.000Z","msg":"一般來說做齊A-D parts 唔係抄野，都會俾中級或以上，我傾向手鬆俾高分少少，因為最後其實都係用你考試個分去做調整。"},{"pid":"3a8892e37f55a5f5e02e2a22d2a54064f18e1532","tid":1436730,"uid":190604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:29:11.000Z","msg":"講得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n推"},{"pid":"6d9f26ba84b667d6ab8c0ddd42de190251c4cf6e","tid":1436730,"uid":119271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:31:22.000Z","msg":"多謝呀sir，如果有日政府真係要改革通識，我地一定仆出黎反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想了解下依家中學生有無政治觸覺？或者主流睇法係點？"},{"pid":"789acad9c0a68966d8829b52d3e7cceabd60a744","tid":1436730,"uid":118311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:31:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"218cea2b0f61f999dd8d2b3c224ed95de0e0d28f","tid":1436730,"uid":91269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:42:48.000Z","msg":"推俾更多人知！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36cddd31a64065417c3a2615eff6363eaab9d2f9","tid":1436730,"uid":71816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:07:28.000Z","msg":"推推 我要真普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6234f9e9a5eb02171fa175344be4d296216875","tid":1436730,"uid":281895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8499d485e4d81f50a923c9ec243a8bc1cb8ef4c1","tid":1436730,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"其實有無人睇過基本法入面講概雙普選？......我睇過但佢話要一個提名委員會認可條友先得，我唔係咁信嗰啲提名委員會"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:12:43.000Z","msg":"提名委員會好似包立法會議員<br />\n<br />\n之前政府搞假普選要提名委員會50%同意先可以參選<br />\n<br />\n如果係10% 就無題<br />\n痴線"},{"pid":"dfc6d97a0cd90fccff06fd88d68ce10f31f01f3a","tid":1436730,"uid":281895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5c6234f9e9a5eb02171fa175344be4d296216875","tid"