0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:20:17.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"a4308b01b24d1cc0949a19f2c43c3662e14cd6d8","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:22:56.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"3b0730c1c4f380c7b32df4d1bac4092bc4130544","tid":1436730,"uid":286859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:25:04.000Z","msg":"香港基本法得50年咋, 過左廿年又黎多次革命定乜呀,到時香港都冇咁既本錢啦。今次香港係終極一戰, 唔好唔記得!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86f7b5bea3975e0f8ea355972bdf11fe003aa4c","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:34:05.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"03c1baf709c5c907929c8ff70f28b4ed203ea09e","tid":1436730,"uid":288397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:54:26.000Z","msg":"我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c907de81ff7d06bf6415aad9b06193113bd8f042","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:57:10.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"eda3064f9cfa219fd6bb727b685770e46e6937a3","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"8499d485e4d81f50a923c9ec243a8bc1cb8ef4c1","tid":1436730,"uid":43468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:56:36.000Z","msg":"其實有無人睇過基本法入面講概雙普選？......我睇過但佢話要一個提名委員會認可條友先得，我唔係咁信嗰啲提名委員會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:01:31.000Z","msg":"其實重點可以放在「廣泛而具代表性」一詞上，只要可以入閘既人唔係完全「欽點」就得。<br />\n其他地方的總統選舉多數是由政黨提名，推舉其代表人物參選。而香港情況有些不同，因為寫明特首唔可以屬於任何政黨，所以唔會由政黨推舉。而係可能由選舉委員會提名。而之前有人提出的「公民提名」也是可以討論的方向。<br />\n當然，呢個暫時未係重點住。但至少我地可以了解先，必要時就可據理力爭了。"},{"pid":"171e4a9381d57f96a5876716810bbcdc5dc55791","tid":1436730,"uid":2248,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78afe00d8ac83271f24a3222530750547d582a46","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1522fc50001fd57aa93bd3009ac2c1782125acc","tid":1436730,"uid":14404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:13:44.000Z","msg":"同政府講落實基本法<br />\n點樣可以避免政府兜返去講廿三條？<br />\n佢哋絕對可以無恥到話依家大部分市民支持全面落實基本法所以依家係時候重推<br />\n到時咪仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:12:22.000Z","msg":"你既問題好好呀。<br />\n當然我地係講緊落實基本法講既雙普選啦，但如果政府真係咁樣玩同屈機，相信全城反對聲會更大，因為大家對23條既反感應比「送中條例」更大既。佢唔可能咁斷章取義。"},{"pid":"3d14ba4af82d14284950729ddb09908532e440a6","tid":1436730,"uid":69275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:15:35.000Z","msg":"非常支持"},{"pid":"88c913c626bf188f4f8cd7004dcc676ba75494f5","tid":1436730,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:26:37.000Z","msg":"push！"},{"pid":"c9088004cfeee61e18b7248e29581411bb1fe79e","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6d9f26ba84b667d6ab8c0ddd42de190251c4cf6e","tid":1436730,"uid":119271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:31:22.000Z","msg":"多謝呀sir，如果有日政府真係要改革通識，我地一定仆出黎反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想了解下依家中學生有無政治觸覺？或者主流睇法係點？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:26:49.000Z","msg":"講真，讀緊書既學生可能同大部分香港人都一樣，好似溫水煮蛙咁，同自己沒有太大關係的，通常都比較冷漠。2014年雨傘會群情洶湧d, 都會關心下參與下；但熱潮過左呢，就會冷卻。2016講選舉啦、DQ議員呀、人大釋法呀、修改議事規則那些，大家明顯好有距離，唔太關心。<br />\n大部分都會關心問唔問政治題，如果問就慘啦，因為覺得最難。我花好多時間講立法會、講拉布，大家都唔會太大興趣。<br />\n咁當然，絕對有對政治較有意識既學生，不過真係佔少數。<br />\n另外，其實通識科只有好少部分直接講政治野，多數都係社會議題、民生問題，d學生反而鐘意多d。<br />\n不過因為今次太大件事，想知想了解既學生又會多d既。但係能夠好有條理咁解釋成件事既就只係少數了。而一些平時比較沈默既學生，對於抗爭及暴力是非常反感的，他們追求的是治安上的和諧。<br />\n利申：教既係band 2 中學。"},{"pid":"9738a81f037018049cbc2753c73d0a74d988b56f","tid":1436730,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:31:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da4fe38b5fdc07391df85b4939fb9b25e47bd08a","tid":1436730,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:33:04.000Z","msg":"釋放義士嘅立場理據係邊？老師可唔可以簡潔咁講一次？每次解釋都好似要兜好大個圈咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec6a9cb5b9d1027a36e1dc3310fbe9fe7b804ca","tid":1436730,"uid":201738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:36:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"07d86b380f9ed9ebd91452b4a89d2e22e33e3309","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:41:13.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"41807db9eb9e7b7eeb9b381288815cd4800263f7","tid":1436730,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c1958ff1c7d2cf4408db91f50b57f45f7d45d73","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:44:11.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"6ceb5f7f632b590ac7dcd07b2e062e23829f0c88","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:46:41.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"1ee99e6756c31d92e7afa4a44ebfa7274b0fbb20","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3b0730c1c4f380c7b32df4d1bac4092bc4130544","tid":1436730,"uid":286859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:25:04.000Z","msg":"香港基本法得50年咋, 過左廿年又黎多次革命定乜呀,到時香港都冇咁既本錢啦。今次香港係終極一戰, 唔好唔記得!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:51:49.000Z","msg":"好問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2047的確係好多人擔心既事，所以也會諗唔明解點要落實基本法，也擔心唔通到時又再爭取過咩。<br />\n<br />\n我既看法係，<br />\n1. 如果特首係全民直選出來的，佢既決策必然需要符合香港人既利益。到差唔多時間，香港就可以同中共談判，討論2047後既安排。民選特首必需企香港人嗰邊。其實當年中英聯合聲明，香港作為主角，但一d話語權都冇。所以要傾既話，香港人一定要有得話事。<br />\n<br />\n2. 其實早在2016年，已經有政黨團體提出「全民制憲 永續基本法」既概念（佢地可能就係大家唔太buy既熱普城）。不過，如果客觀咁睇，呢個其實都係一個可行既方法。永續個「50年不變」，即50年無限♾，全部都係法理之內既野，目的係維護一國兩制之餘，又做到中港分隔。<br />\n<br />\n當然上述兩個方法既前題都係有「雙普選」，咁先有得傾。就算冇雙普選，都要立法會內有足夠既聲音（要2/3議員同意）先可以推動到上面所講既野。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d693752c3f25379078f0a0f242b63e798b9c7b96","tid":1436730,"uid":291998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:55:50.000Z","msg":"分析得好清楚！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7605f347369cc5abf77f2a86e87d2d2089aad092","tid":1436730,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CA49pWr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCA49pWr.jpg&h=427a69f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G5LHKWs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG5LHKWs.jpg&h=60c8f395&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04f25e056e23255d546d2e5fe9463cb8e4afb722","tid":1436730,"uid":210612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:57:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648105022d2bc3bb2fabdbfa50e471e2d0393ddb","tid":1436730,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:58:13.000Z","msg":"又嚟屌時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7029cd4f5bc8eb01a4c869560178938ba92e0523","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9088004cfeee61e18b7248e29581411bb1fe79e","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6d9f26ba84b667d6ab8c0ddd42de190251c4cf6e","tid":1436730,"uid":119271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:31:22.000Z","msg":"多謝呀sir，如果有日政府真係要改革通識，我地一定仆出黎反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想