:{"pid":"648105022d2bc3bb2fabdbfa50e471e2d0393ddb","tid":1436730,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:58:13.000Z","msg":"又嚟屌時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:24:39.000Z","msg":"唔係話「屌」既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係分享返自己有呢個看法啫，同埋都有唔少人會問「時代革命」係咩。<br />\n都係嗰句：「不篤灰 不割𥱊」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e291efed5291dd0a4b22d01621c9beca66469b17","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:49:29.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"222dcb92e8e27b74526b8eb2eabcdb34130ce5c5","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T15:55:09.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"913b034b3a8d0bc930ced7e827d2d409521d739c","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:01:00.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"4d7826639ceb64bd57ec3e86bd2ac24c047b9cfc","tid":1436730,"uid":271068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15a2ec5c5c01a29466e5ece0a6803a663639cd54","tid":1436730,"uid":215341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:55:48.000Z","msg":"雨傘革命就係革命，時代革命就唔係革命？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:08:02.000Z","msg":"雨傘革命失敗了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9pxocj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9pxocj.jpg&h=a00251ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8c422df9dec4bbfefe44e9e5b4498c3066ef0d4f","tid":1436730,"uid":271068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd80ae125f27c0bddbaabad6e63eda50e2f52277","tid":1436730,"uid":291279,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:55:47.000Z","msg":"文章有理有節，值得嘉許。<br />\n「光復香港，時代革命」的口號已經深入民心，只能夠是有一個更好的口號才能取而代之。我倒是不認為時代革命這四個字真的是觸動了某些天條。這句話是任由各人去詮釋的。欲加之罪，何患無詞？倒不如是加入一些具體目標在口號裏面，藉此去詮釋抗爭者所說的時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n沒有暴徒，只有暴政<br />\n落實普選，追究黑警<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:08:54.000Z","msg":"明知欲加之罪，何苦焦頭爛額，為敵軍上子彈"},{"pid":"94b71aec7be2fb0acb6ccce1a64c9adc0a694253","tid":1436730,"uid":271068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c422df9dec4bbfefe44e9e5b4498c3066ef0d4f","tid":1436730,"uid":271068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd80ae125f27c0bddbaabad6e63eda50e2f52277","tid":1436730,"uid":291279,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:55:47.000Z","msg":"文章有理有節，值得嘉許。<br />\n「光復香港，時代革命」的口號已經深入民心，只能夠是有一個更好的口號才能取而代之。我倒是不認為時代革命這四個字真的是觸動了某些天條。這句話是任由各人去詮釋的。欲加之罪，何患無詞？倒不如是加入一些具體目標在口號裏面，藉此去詮釋抗爭者所說的時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n沒有暴徒，只有暴政<br />\n落實普選，追究黑警<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:08:54.000Z","msg":"明知欲加之罪，何苦焦頭爛額，為敵軍上子彈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:09:40.000Z","msg":"Be Wise, Be 重就輕"},{"pid":"312162b5f6dc36133fc6afb80fe1f099caf4637e","tid":1436730,"uid":119271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9088004cfeee61e18b7248e29581411bb1fe79e","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6d9f26ba84b667d6ab8c0ddd42de190251c4cf6e","tid":1436730,"uid":119271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:31:22.000Z","msg":"多謝呀sir，如果有日政府真係要改革通識，我地一定仆出黎反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想了解下依家中學生有無政治觸覺？或者主流睇法係點？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:26:49.000Z","msg":"講真，讀緊書既學生可能同大部分香港人都一樣，好似溫水煮蛙咁，同自己沒有太大關係的，通常都比較冷漠。2014年雨傘會群情洶湧d, 都會關心下參與下；但熱潮過左呢，就會冷卻。2016講選舉啦、DQ議員呀、人大釋法呀、修改議事規則那些，大家明顯好有距離，唔太關心。<br />\n大部分都會關心問唔問政治題，如果問就慘啦，因為覺得最難。我花好多時間講立法會、講拉布，大家都唔會太大興趣。<br />\n咁當然，絕對有對政治較有意識既學生，不過真係佔少數。<br />\n另外，其實通識科只有好少部分直接講政治野，多數都係社會議題、民生問題，d學生反而鐘意多d。<br />\n不過因為今次太大件事，想知想了解既學生又會多d既。但係能夠好有條理咁解釋成件事既就只係少數了。而一些平時比較沈默既學生，對於抗爭及暴力是非常反感的，他們追求的是治安上的和諧。<br />\n利申：教既係band 2 中學。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:15:53.000Z","msg":"靚女miss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學生的確覺得政治離自己好遠，但要相信自己教既野會成為種子，成為佢地思想資源。我中二初次認識六四都無咩感覺，但之後認識到中國政治敗壞，香港失去核心價值，再遇上國教就醒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋呢次事件根源始終係年輕一代對中共不信任，唔知播下鏗鏘集既陽光司法，或者講下社會信用系統，會唔會令到學生比較容易理解社會上所謂激烈既行為？<br />\n<br />\nsorry if 班門弄斧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己都想行教育條路，想學下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d2592d334faa04d60a4601ab69b1847eb46c88","tid":1436730,"uid":262445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:19:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b30ae0726bc2fcb07fcb871e1c560d36f96f8aa0","tid":1436730,"uid":274469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:21:24.000Z","msg":"整體都同意，但唔同意要改口號"},{"pid":"6100975656a7c695797d6bfdd16cf7ad5d99c068","tid":1436730,"uid":43381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:23:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32db6e3fd403c8bcb8e6851dc508e5d101d2e89a","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"da4fe38b5fdc07391df85b4939fb9b25e47bd08a","tid":1436730,"uid":265443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:33:04.000Z","msg":"釋放義士嘅立場理據係邊？老師可唔可以簡潔咁講一次？每次解釋都好似要兜好大個圈咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:37:04.000Z","msg":"呢個涉及好多法律問題，而香港一直重視「司法獨立」，理論上法庭既判決唔可以有政治考量。<br />\n要釋放義士，簡單既當然就係「撤銷暴動定性」，不過呢個就防唔到「非法集結」、「襲警」呢d控罪。<br />\n也有人提出司法覆核，話「非法集結」同「暴動罪」係違反基本法同國際人權公約。呢樣嘢長毛梁國雄曾經做過，（佢覆核左公安條例）不過佢係失敗左既。<br />\n至於「襲警罪」，好睇個情況係點，如果有前因後果睇到係自衛就容易冇事，同埋警察冇識別既話可以拗唔知佢係警察。所以影左既片作為呈堂証供是非常重要的。<br />\n另外，一係就係律政司唔作檢控，因為之前都有律政司既律師發聲話呢d係唔公義既政治檢控黎。<br />\n再理想一d既係，普選特首利用特赦令，釋放所有政治犯。<br />\n都可以參考埋台灣太陽花，抗爭者被判無罪，判詞指「他們的做法屬最後必要手段」，法院批評立委做法有誤才導致示威者利用抗爭手法，情況全屬合理。當然，台灣的法治與香港仍有一段距離，她們的做法未必能適用於香港。"},{"pid":"8b6bb76a329706547d90fc76fdf8fb7671788a04","tid":1436730,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:40:06.000Z","msg":"手太快，禁錯正評"},{"pid":"6d0ae1d6e468427cfbb3f1ba2e744f9f0b1e93bd","tid":1436730,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:45:56.000Z","msg":"做得通識阿sir<br />\n仲撚天真過d 學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲信一國兩制<br />\n如果要落實基本法 廿三條都係基本法入面<br />\n<br />\n一國兩制意思就係要先有一國，再有兩制<br />\n一國＞兩制<br />\n咁樣咪姐係做中國殖民地"},{"pid":"610d518cbf13ad68064ab4bd93b65b041a1aef42","tid":1436730,"uid":50647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06b60397bb3f624f69ae3bfd531af8eb219c23a9","tid":1436730,"uid":266011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:46:48.000Z","msg":"唔該諗埋：<br />\n點樣實行港獨？<br />\n解散左政府邊個上？<br />\n老解出硬點解決？<br />\n結論：不如諗左雙普先"},{"pid":"b0c43b117f851fab7b8feda1845fb5e8fb972593","tid":1436730,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:49:00.000Z","msg":"時代革命意思就新時代新思想既人推翻舊時代舊思想<br />\n其實好闊，任你演繹"},{"pid":"ecff58c0c20742b7a7414d7c588952b7b4e3f9a4","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6d0ae1d6e468427cfbb3f1ba2e744f9f0b1e93bd","tid":1436730,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:45:56.000Z","msg":"做得通識阿sir<br />\n仲撚天真過d 學生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲信一國兩制<br />\n如果要落實基本法 廿三條都係基本法入面<br />\n<br />\n一國兩制意思就係要先有一國，再有兩制<br />\n一國＞兩制<br />\n咁樣咪姐係做中國殖民地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:04:55.000Z","msg":"咁就要知道香港既地位係咩。如果只係中國殖民地，一早同你講係中國城市，唔係特區。<br />\n中共一直靠緊香港兩大樣野：<br />\n1. 國際地位<br />\n2. 司法獨立<br />\n中共依家經濟開始唔得，面對「產能過剩」同「製造業轉型」問題，內需唔夠，一定要「走出去」，所以要靠香港呢個中間人幫佢，「一帶一路」「大灣區」都係咁。所以佢想繼續搞經濟，就要依靠香港呢個「特區」既地位。所以現在就係爭取既好時機。<br />\n<br />\n或者大家都好想做到獨立，但其實如果有民選既特首，已經可以實踐到「自治」的程度，而且又不需要重新建立國際地位。講真，如果香港獨立，而中共又仍然存在的話，國際社會又會唔會承認呢？<br />\n暫時只要繼續做「特區」，落實「自治」，到中共唔掂既時候，咁我地就同獨立冇分別。這是只是是時間的問題。"},{"pid":"f30a26e1f60effe4ee8e549e8b9b98ef3b1bbaee","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"312162b5f6dc36133fc6afb80fe1f099caf4637e","tid":1436730,"uid":119271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9088004cfeee61e18b7248e29581411bb1fe79e","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"6d9f26ba84b667d6ab8c0ddd42de190251c4cf6e","tid":1436730,"uid":119271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:31:22.000Z","msg":"多謝呀sir，如果有日政府真係要改革通識，我地一定仆出黎反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想了解下依家中學生有無政治觸覺？或者主流睇法係點？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T14:26:49.000Z","msg":"講真，讀緊書既學生可能同大部分香港人都一樣，好似溫水煮蛙咁，同自己沒有太大關係的，通常都比較冷漠。2014年雨傘會群情洶湧d, 都會關心下參與下；但熱潮過左呢，就會冷卻。2016講選舉啦、DQ議員呀、人大釋法呀、修改議事規則那些，大家明顯好有距離，唔太關心。<br />\n大部分都會關心問唔問政治題，如果問就慘啦，因為覺得最難。我花好多時間講立法會、講拉布，大家都唔會太大興趣。<br />\n咁當然，絕對有對政治較有意識既學生，不過真係佔少數。<br />\n另外，其實通識科只有好少部分直接講政治野，多數都係社會議題、民生問題，d學生反而鐘意多d。<br />\n不過因為今次太大件事，想知想了解既學生又會多d既。但係能夠好有條理咁解釋成件事既就只係少數了。而一些平時比較沈默既學生，對於抗爭及暴力是非常反感的，他們追求的是治安上的和諧。<br />\n利申：教既係band 2 中學。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:15:53.000Z","msg":"靚女miss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學生的確覺得政治離自己好遠，但要相信自己教既野會成為種子，成為佢地思想資源。我中二初次認識六四都無咩感覺，但之後認識到中國政治敗壞，香港失去核心價值，再遇上國教就醒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋呢次事件根源始終係年輕一代對中共不信任，唔知播下鏗鏘集既陽光司法，或者講下社會信用系統，會唔會令到學生比較容易理解社會上所謂激烈既行為？<br />\n<br />\nsorry if 班門弄斧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己都想行教育條路，想學下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:15:01.000Z","msg":"行教育呢，很不容易啊。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係教通識就更加冇運行了，最好識教一兩科旁身。<br />\n而且做老師要有使命感，真係架，好多野唔係即時見效，係好長好長既投資。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你講得岩，有d種子係會種左喺學生度既，總有一天會結果的。<br />\n不過，香港既教育制度太重考試，學生唔熱愛學習，有時真係無可厚非。當然，成績絕對不是一切。 如果你有機會做到老師既話，記住多關心學生，要多了解下一代既看法，對社會先有幫作架。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加油吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9ef3a2de95e913d2db71d08fcd007698fe4b21e","tid":1436730,"uid":31609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:20:41.000Z","msg":"好！"},{"pid":"9df69e15144568feec2afb4c02fe954c12ec1826","tid":1436730,"uid":31609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:23:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2f51a9a93e5a765638fa220cf3549bd9eecbd5d","tid":1436730,"uid":98273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:24:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"181d51c782b0320e81fe28f009bdfa24752e3f39","tid":1436730,"uid":31609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:24:42.000Z","msg":"落真雙普選"},{"pid":"57eba5244eb42ac4045bc81502918970ea7952b5","tid":1436730,"uid":134924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:25:15.000Z","msg":"有用 推"},{"pid":"32f7001b0b87d45bf53a7b38e1342acfc9bf444a","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:35:47.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"61afa41d19d82d2fd0d68e299fa4bf0f0266f491","tid":1436730,"uid":98273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:56:30.000Z","msg":"又推"},{"pid":"d3e9fcc49960f4f4bd2a7e276074b93bdd678f90","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:40:52.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"6e38aefe4eeed990a5565597ceb2b3db9810c19b","tid":1436730,"uid":266011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"610d518cbf13ad68064ab4bd93b65b041a1aef42","tid":1436730,"uid":50647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06b60397bb3f624f69ae3bfd531af8eb219c23a9","tid":1436730,"uid":266011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:46:48.000Z","msg":"唔該諗埋：<br />\n點樣實行港獨？<br />\n解散左政府邊個上？<br />\n老解出硬點解決？<br />\n結論：不如諗左雙普先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a417e3b321c392051423523beed04de6708ffbff","tid":1436730,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:02:23.000Z","msg":"光復香港 支持一國兩制<br />\n落實雙普選 追究黑警濫暴"},{"pid":"311e832197a578bd88cc00e1acf0a0061a928006","tid":1436730,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:03:19.000Z","msg":"光復香港 支持一國兩制<br />\n落實雙普選 追究黑警濫暴"},{"pid":"a8f3fdf6b332abae131a2fb6e89a511d627e5cf4","tid":1436730,"uid":240802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T19:17:49.000Z","msg":"咁反送中 撒回悪法呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16400634e54c4e6e67413d9239ba1304ea63455","tid":1436730,"uid":263525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"070021b40ba19a5c1336518fc18a900d0ffa1901","tid":1436730,"uid":246354,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:54:01.000Z","msg":"你地比ies個評分標準係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T20:03:49.000Z","msg":"個個老師都唔同。但排個名次再按dse成績比例去分配排第幾拎幾分就容易了。至少不同老師排出來不會差太遠。<br />\n<br />\n研集要選對題。具爭議性題目，難度較高，因為涉及的價值取態必然具道德上的可議性。你要將不同立場背後的道德理論找出來簡述，並應用到不同持份者身上，再進行批判或檢視。如果不是名校，通常不獲批。因為一講漏就中下品<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後，當然係對題目的全貌理解。比如說，講到垃圾分類，有甚麼相關的持份者？<br />\n上游的生產商，包裝商，中游的消費者，市民，零售商，下游的垃圾收集商，回收商。以及整合所有持份者的政府部門。還有每個持份者的文化取態與習慣。齊料，上品。講漏中下品。<br />\n<br />\n分析部分，若分析政策，最好是針對全持份者做沙盤推演。成功並輔以外國例子或高汁第一手資料搜集就上品。有任何缺漏就中下品。<br />\n<br />\n建議方面，你一定要有立場，而且要從理論和實務層面支持自己立場。若用推演法去推論，必須符合邏輯，若用歸納法來做則要有大量論據十卜。做到上品。若倒亂推演歸納，你要看你老師是否腦袋清晰了。有腦老師必會批為下品。若立場太偏離主流，論證論據和論述必須更完整，這也是最多老師評分有不同的地方。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大概係咁，好鬼眼訓。。。"},{"pid":"9a2bec69bfc413e2ccc3e9a5174d6b3adc57194c","tid":1436730,"uid":31623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T00:52:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c357f334fd8b17ae2b5c6dad3aa90c76f58d9b0f","tid":1436730,"uid":264992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:06:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98363f1d9a86d0d4a280ae041fbfaa8b0f38ab5d","tid":1436730,"uid":285413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd80ae125f27c0bddbaabad6e63eda50e2f52277","tid":1436730,"uid":291279,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T10:55:47.000Z","msg":"文章有理有節，值得嘉許。<br />\n「光復香港，時代革命」的口號已經深入民心，只能夠是有一個更好的口號才能取而代之。我倒是不認為時代革命這四個字真的是觸動了某些天條。這句話是任由各人去詮釋的。欲加之罪，何患無詞？倒不如是加入一些具體目標在口號裏面，藉此去詮釋抗爭者所說的時代革命。<br />\n<br />\n沒有暴徒，只有暴政<br />\n落實普選，追究黑警<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:26:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5vcGjDs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5vcGjDs.png&h=da9cd713&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4a5ebd879a498a41dfcd879a4bc653467bb983ed","tid":1436730,"uid":184096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:28:46.000Z","msg":"但我更支持大家解釋咩係時代革命<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n［8.10大埔尋貓］走失名為豬油（or自由）嘅貓咪，希望大家一齊幫手入嚟大埔搵貓<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1438472\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1438472</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d2bc41250421e675f9f1a209abac35e8920db588","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:52:18.000Z","msg":"想澄清返，我指既落實基本法，之前講得唔清楚，就係落實<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">基本法中既雙普選</span></strong>。呢個係第一步。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後，就係好多人即刻會擔心2046呀、23條、人大釋法呢d。<br />\n咁第二步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實有一種玩法，就係「全民制憲」或者「全民修憲」。<br />\n<br />\n呢個概念在1998年已經有民主派人士提出，主張「修改《基本法》中阻礙民主進程，限制人權的條例，並交由港人透過全民投票表決。」不過之後就不了了之左。<br />\n<br />\n2016年選舉，又有人提出「全民制憲」，主張修改甚至重寫基本法，令基本法成為真正保障香港人利益既憲法。同樣地，呢個理念俾好多香港人認為天芳夜譚，所以得唔到支持。<br />\n<br />\n到左今日既局勢，如果落實雙普選之後提倡「全民制憲」或「修憲」，或者可以釋除大家既疑慮。實際既做法可以好多，例如「永續」某些條文、增加或減少一些條文、甚至係修改條文，原則係「全民參與」的成份，在港人利益的前題下來制定憲法，而重點是呢樣都係「一國兩制」框架下進行，是合乎法理的做法。這也是實際的政治操作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />或者用一個比喻：<br />\n中共係業主，香港係租客，租約係基本法。我要繼續住，就要傾續租。之前佢強勢，我簽左d唔著數既條款；而家業主開始弱勢，而我又係一個超優質租客，佢好想租俾我，咁我就可以乘機增減有利我自己既條款啦。我依然住喺度，所以我唔會毀左份約。<br />\n到左一日，業主瓜埋，我玩埋逆權侵佔，成功埋。不費吹灰之力。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n常存盼望 佢總會瓜的。"},{"pid":"37da1a59ead390bb977c1121c7a575e7f09610ea","tid":1436730,"uid":122084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T01:59:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0ee31141d0786470b98ae0e793781895c0f3390","tid":1436730,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:53:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5d4f212f52878c5054222e7490f62233720490ea","tid":1436730,"uid":285858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T02:56:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"824d43a1f0e402ad53e0ac31bdeb0cfcd9ac1053","tid":1436730,"uid":271669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e38aefe4eeed990a5565597ceb2b3db9810c19b","tid":1436730,"uid":266011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"610d518cbf13ad68064ab4bd93b65b041a1aef42","tid":1436730,"uid":50647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"06b60397bb3f624f69ae3bfd531af8eb219c23a9","tid":1436730,"uid":266011,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:46:48.000Z","msg":"唔該諗埋：<br />\n點樣實行港獨？<br />\n解散左政府邊個上？<br />\n老解出硬點解決？<br />\n結論：不如諗左雙普先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:35:05.000Z","msg":"我相信2047中共已倒台<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xsfpNX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xsfpNX.jpg&h=6b32ae32&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83948f94933644d27cb534b78815890fcfc0682d","tid":1436730,"uid":98273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:31:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a8199ca11b4f2372b64a2ea2497c1427ae1d0849","tid":1436730,"uid":45035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a90946338443c9ca4bc1358d54e9aab9c4cb86a4","tid":1436730,"uid":8948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:41:17.000Z","msg":"因此，我認為要「光復香港」就已經足夠了。<br />\n<br />\n但如果講「革命」，大家都會變得敏感，是否推翻政權？咁係咪建立新政權？或者有新政制？ 國際對我地既支持就會變得猶豫。<br />\n<br />\n點解人地話你搞革命就要自我閹割???<br />\n由下而上既改變，就係革命<br />\n而家就係要革除呢個腐敗既制度<br />\n呢個由冇民主造就既制度，包括選行政長官，立法會結構，DQ 等等<br />\n<br />\n點解永遠都係自我閹割? 咁樣爭取到乜野?<br />\n<br />\n時代革命係講緊處於呢個時代既人，由3歲到80歲，只要你既思想係支持，你都係呢個時代既一份子，你都係想係香港爭取自由、民主同公義既革命既一份子"},{"pid":"49d0774a7cca458246b6b9b7fb2cd5037c3d06a2","tid":1436730,"uid":266011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"824d43a1f0e402ad53e0ac31bdeb0cfcd9ac1053","tid":1436730,"uid":271669,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e38aefe4eeed990a5565597ceb2b3db9810c19b","tid":1436730,"uid":266011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"610d518cbf13ad68064ab4bd93b65b041a1aef42","tid":1436730,"uid":50647,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:46:48.000Z","msg":"唔該諗埋：<br />\n點樣實行港獨？<br />\n解散左政府邊個上？<br />\n老解出硬點解決？<br />\n結論：不如諗左雙普先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T18:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:35:05.000Z","msg":"我相信2047中共已倒台<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6xsfpNX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6xsfpNX.jpg&h=6b32ae32&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:13:08.000Z","msg":"望就咁望啦～"},{"pid":"4b7d65ded8177d5d547e5083fcaafa638d252805","tid":1436730,"uid":98273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T07:05:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f91a6bbab89559739cba237d42db2d0d10d1908f","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:13:38.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"92ac91601fb0c6f96cb3dd167ae6fda6a3eff260","tid":1436730,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:15:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8b09063f59f0efee6eb2f671e45349a3b45f291","tid":1436730,"uid":304174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T10:46:44.000Z","msg":"時代革命真係唔係個個都明，<br />\n讚成口號應該要一睇就明。<br />\n好多人見到革命就覺得係搞事，如果用改革，革新之類會好啲。"},{"pid":"f9abe4e369c6b6cc47fcc0c21313ccc71877d484","tid":1436730,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T11:05:10.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f2d652a2b0df06f83f472903e699a1a95f0a41c4","tid":1436730,"uid":1524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:03:04.000Z","msg":"push！"},{"pid":"58831ec0de35938239400da97fed653c79558fbc","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:37:32.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"8ca1d5c67c321cb59def8f38ea22986833b78623","tid":1436730,"uid":289991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T16:41:15.000Z","msg":"認同，清晰，推！"},{"pid":"75fb8b4d6130aeac994f937e210d8478d403889d","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:25:51.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"1f73602faa37e02aaa46ba0561fd88a391da7a7c","tid":1436730,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:27:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e053865d42ed350ae63d8dceb360384777d3a958","tid":1436730,"uid":267028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:41:46.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"f953bf68f0a869a00c23b02807c0e7323d6bd92c","tid":1436730,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T17:44:35.000Z","msg":"推"}]}